  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cash &amp; Voucher transfers for vulnerable famine affected population in Panyijiar County, Unity State.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Activity1.Rapid Assesment to identify the needs of the community.
Activity2.Printing of the Cash Vouchers in denomination of 250ssp and 500ssp.
Activity3.Community mobilization and discussion on beneficiary selection critteria.
Activity4.Identification,registration and verification of beneficiaries list.
Activity5.Distribution of cash voucher/cash transfers to 600HH famine affected IDPs, returnees and Host communities.
Activity 6.Post Distribution monitoring and reporting.
Activity 7. Installation of solar system in the PHCC facility
Activity 8. Fencing of established demonstration farms.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The targeted households will have accesst o food and other basic households needs.
Increased purchasing power of the direct project beneficiaries to acess basic commodities from the local market.</narrative>
  </description>
